 Fifi Cooper has been shown the door by her no-nonsense boss Kgosi Mahumapelo of Ambitiouz Records allegedly for disrespecting him, bringing the name of the company into disrepute, going AWOL and disrespecting her colleagues, amongst others.Mahumapelo confirmed Fifi Cooper, real name Refiloe Mooketsi, was no longer with their stable as she had breached her contract."I can confirm that Fifi Cooper is no longer with Ambitiouz but these are matters of breach of contract that we can't discuss. The issue is being handled by our legal team, so it's sub judice," he said.TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE 